Description: # coi: see output/input status of all sub-folders
        
        This tool batch run 2 shell commands on all sub-folders and display the outputs
        succinctly.
        
        ## example
        
        Suppose the folder structure
        ```
        jobs-folder
        ├── sub1
        │   ├── 1.input
        │   ├── 1.output
        │   └── 2.input
        ├── sub2
        │   ├── 1.input
        │   └── 2.input
        ├── sub3
        │   ├── 1.input
        │   ├── 1.output
        │   ├── 2.input
        │   └── 2.output
        └── sub4
            ├── 1.input
            └── 1.output
        ```
        
        ```bash
        coi -o ll *.output
        coi -i ll *.input
        coi jobs-folder
        ```
        
        ```bash
        sub1 (1 / 2)
        sub2 (0 / 2)
        sub3 (2 / 2)
        sub4 (1 / 1)
        ```
        
